import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { AlertTriangle, Clock, TrendingUp, Filter, Download, Search, AlertCircle, Package, Eye } from 'lucide-react'; const ReviewSpamPage = () => { const [selectedAlert, setSelectedAlert] = useState(spamReviews[0]); const [filterPriority, setFilterPriority] = useState('all'); const spamReviews = [ { id: 'RS001', title: 'Fake review campaign detected', description: 'Multiple 5-star reviews from new accounts within 24 hours', productId: 'P987654321', reviewCount: 47, category: 'Review Manipulation', timeframe: '24 hours ago', riskScore: 94, priority: 'high', riskLevel: 'High', investigationBrief: 'Detected coordinated review campaign with 47 suspicious reviews posted by newly created accounts within a 24-hour window. All reviews show similar language patterns and 5-star ratings.', riskIndicators: ['new_account_activity', 'similar_language_patterns', 'timing_clustering', 'rating_manipulation'], subAgentResults: { languageAnalysis: { score: 92, confidence: 'High' }, accountPatternAnalysis: { score: 96, confidence: 'High' }, temporalAnalysis: { score: 88, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'RS002', title: 'Incentivized review scheme', description: 'Reviews mentioning free products or compensation', productId: 'P456789012', reviewCount: 23, category: 'Incentivized Reviews', timeframe: '3 days ago', riskScore: 76, priority: 'medium', riskLevel: 'Medium', investigationBrief: 'Identified reviews containing language suggesting compensation or free products in exchange for positive reviews, violating platform guidelines.', riskIndicators: ['compensation_mentions', 'free_product_references', 'guideline_violations'], subAgentResults: { languageAnalysis: { score: 82, confidence: 'High' }, accountPatternAnalysis: { score: 68, confidence: 'Medium' }, temporalAnalysis: { score: 74, confidence: 'Medium' } } }, { id: 'RS003', title: 'Competitor review bombing', description: 'Sudden influx of 1-star reviews with generic complaints', productId: 'P123456789', reviewCount: 15, category: 'Negative Campaign', timeframe: '5 days ago', riskScore: 58, priority: 'medium', riskLevel: 'Medium', investigationBrief: 'Detected coordinated negative review campaign with generic complaints and similar writing patterns, potentially from competitors.', riskIndicators: ['negative_clustering', 'generic_complaints', 'coordinated_timing'], subAgentResults: { languageAnalysis: { score: 64, confidence: 'Medium' }, accountPatternAnalysis: { score: 55, confidence: 'Low' }, temporalAnalysis: { score: 61, confidence: 'Medium' } } }, { id: 'RS004', title: 'Bot-generated reviews', description: 'Reviews showing AI-generated content patterns', productId: 'P789123456', reviewCount: 8, category: 'Automated Content', timeframe: '1 week ago', riskScore: 42, priority: 'low', riskLevel: 'Low', investigationBrief: 'Reviews exhibit characteristics of AI-generated content with repetitive sentence structures and unusual phrasing patterns.', riskIndicators: ['ai_generated_patterns', 'repetitive_structure'], subAgentResults: { languageAnalysis: { score: 78, confidence: 'High' }, accountPatternAnalysis: { score: 28, confidence: 'Low' }, temporalAnalysis: { score: 35, confidence: 'Low' } } } ]; const filteredAlerts = filterPriority === 'all' ? spamReviews : spamReviews.filter(alert => alert.priority === filterPriority); const handleAction = (id, action) => { console.log(`Action taken on ${id}: ${action}`); // Add actual implementation here }; const getPriorityColor = (priority) => { switch (priority) { case 'high': return 'bg-red-500 text-white'; case 'medium': return 'bg-orange-500 text-white'; case 'low': return 'bg-green-500 text-white'; default: return 'bg-gray-500 text-white'; } }; const getRiskScoreColor = (score) => { if (score >= 80) return 'text-red-400'; if (score >= 60) return 'text-orange-400'; return 'text-green-400'; }; return (

Review Spam Detection

Identifying fake reviews and manipulation campaigns

High Risk Cases

{spamReviews.filter(r => r.priority === 'high').length}

Medium Risk Cases

{spamReviews.filter(r => r.priority === 'medium').length}

Low Risk Cases

{spamReviews.filter(r => r.priority === 'low').length}

{filteredAlerts.map((review) => (
setSelectedAlert(review)} >

{review.id}

{review.priority.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + review.priority.slice(1)}

{review.title}

{review.description}

Product ID: {review.productId}
Reviews Flagged: {review.reviewCount}
Category: {review.category}
{review.timeframe}
Risk Score:
{review.riskScore}%
))}
); }; const InvestigationPanel = ({ selectedAlert, handleAction }) => { const getRiskColor = (riskLevel) => { switch (riskLevel) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600/90 text-white border-red-400'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500/90 text-black border-yellow-400'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500/90 text-white border-green-400'; default: return 'bg-neutral-700 text-white border-neutral-600'; } }; return (

Investigation Details

{selectedAlert.title}

{selectedAlert.riskLevel} Risk

{selectedAlert.description}

Investigation Brief

{selectedAlert.investigationBrief}

Risk Indicators

{selectedAlert.riskIndicators.map((indicator, index) => ( {indicator.replace(/_/g, ' ').toUpperCase()} ))}

Sub-Agent Analysis

{Object.entries(selectedAlert.subAgentResults).map(([agent, result]) => (
{agent.replace(/([A-Z])/g, ' $1').trim()}
{result.score}%
{result.confidence} Confidence
))}
); }; export default ReviewSpamPage;
